This program will launch a webpage consisting of all the movies given in entertainment_center.py. On top of user rating
given in entertainment_center.py, it also looks up the rating on imdb and displays it. If you hover over any of the
movie posters you should see the movie plot. If you click on the movies, its trailer would be played.

To run the program, keep the following scripts in the same directory
- movie_trailer.py
- entertainment_center.py
- fresh_tomatoes.py

Run
python entertainment_center.py